    <section id="faq" class="section orange">
        <div class="container" style="padding-top:20px">
            <h4>About MyDay</h4>
            <!-- start: Accordion -->
            <div class="accordion" id="accordion2">

                <div class="accordion-group">
                    <div class="accordion-heading">
                        <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion2" href="#collapseTwo">
                            <i class="icon-plus"></i> What is MyDay?
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-body collapse">
                        <div class="accordion-inner">
                            MyDay is an internet-based survey study of wellbeing at work. The surveys measure how an employee feels while going about their day-to-day tasks.
                            <br />
                            <br />
                            MyDay surveys give valuable insight into the working day experience, which provides direction to improve wellbeing at work.
                            <br />
                            <br />
                            MyDay is led by Professor Rhema Vaithianathan at Auckland University of Technology, New Zealand.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-group">
                    <div class="accordion-heading">
                        <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion2" href="#collapseThree">
                            <i class="icon-plus"></i> Who can participate in this study?
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-body collapse">
                        <div class="accordion-inner">
                            MyDay surveys are customised for different workplaces and industries. Current work includes doctors, social workers and architects.
                            <br />
                            <br />
                            If you are interested to measure wellbeing at your workplace, please contact
                            <a href="mailto:larissa.lorimer@aut.ac.nz">larissa.lorimer@aut.ac.nz</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-group">
                    <div class="accordion-heading">
                        <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion2" href="#collapse4">
                            <i class="icon-plus"></i> Will my information be secure?
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapse4" class="accordion-body collapse">
                        <div class="accordion-inner">
                            Protecting your privacy is important to us. Personal data and survey responses are kept in secure servers at Auckland University of Technology in New Zealand. Personal information is stored separately from survey responses.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                @*<div class="accordion-group">
                    <div class="accordion-heading">
                        <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion2" href="#collapse5">
